title: Ohana Beach Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, British, English, Hawaiian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Surf cafe overlooking Great Western Beach with views over Newquay Bay from the cliff top terrace. Modern British cuisine with a Hawaiian/surf influence. Food is cooked to order and includes veg choices like the sweet potato burger, salads, sandwiches, and mezze plates. Evening menu changes weekly and might include tofu satay skewers and curry; BYOB. Free Wi-Fi, dogs welcome.
